name: temps
description: Simple menubar application based on Electron with actual weather information and forecast.

packageJSON.name: temps
packageJSON.description: A simple but smart menubar weather app

scripts.build: npm run build:osx && npm run build:win && npm run build:linux
scripts.package: npm run package:win32 && npm run package:win64 && npm run package:osx && npm run package:linux
scripts.package:linux: cd dist/ && zip -r Temps_Linux_x64.zip Temps-linux-x64 && zip -r Temps_Linux_ia32.zip Temps-linux-ia32 && cd ../

releases.name: Shower rain
releases.body:
- switch between 24h/12h clock #24
- change manually the color (black/white) of the tray icon if necessary #23
- fix bad snow animation looping #21 
- further style improvements #23, #19

releases.name: Smoke
releases.body:
- Got several problems using the [Google Maps Timezone API](https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/timezone) with so much traffic
  --> disabled timezone support for now until I will find a better solution 
- Fixed snow animation
- Some style improvements

releases.name: Moderate rain
releases.body:
- Fix timezone summertime bug
- Rain improvement
- Windows icon improvements
- Code clean up and build status
- Style adjustments

releases.name: Clear sky
releases.body:
- Further usability & style improvements
- Geolocation usage (in settings or use <kbd>Cmd</kbd> + <kbd>G</kbd>)

releases.name: Moderate rain
releases.body:
- Fix forecast graph bug

releases.name: Broken clouds
releases.body:
- Improve hourly forecast graph with weather icon and usability update
- Optional start at login available
- Advanced taskbar icons
- Support keyboard functions
- Number counting animation
- Save favorite city
- Random city feature
- Auto updater on app start
- Code improvements and clean up
- Bugfixes

releases.name: Few clouds
releases.body:
- Visit the new [landing page](https://jackd248.github.io/temps/) 
- Solving font problem
- Improved error handling
- Added snow and loading animation
- Parsing time and date of selected city by [Google Maps Time Zone API](https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/timezone/intro)
- Style improvements

releases.name: Light rain
releases.body:
- Error handling
- Menubar OSX dark mode icon fix
